DEATHRUN_DOCKS
--------------------

Made by Hai (Pirate ship by OEM and some random stuff by Remikseri_fin, for example some texture choises)


INCLUDES:
---------

- 31 CT and 2 Terrorist spawnpoints
- 17 traps
- Two "secret" grenades
- Three normal endings (and one secret)
- Skybox

---------

Deathrun_docks is a basic deathrun map and it includes 17 triggerable traps. Counter-terrorist start from the land and the terrorist start from inside a hall (or something...). Traps can be used again after 20 second delay. I can't figure out anything more to say, so download, rate and COMMENT!
